  "text": "1. 5d field theories can be constructed both from brane configurations (webs) [CITATION_1] [CITATION_2] and by compactifying M theory on a Calabi-Yau (CY) threefold while decoupling gravity by shrinking a 4 cycle. It was conjectured that there is a mapping between webs and Calabi-Yau manifolds.",
